ce/Batavia_Downs\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Batavia_Downs\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"BACKGROUND:Pair indicted on multiple charges following Genesee County sergeant's death  Members of law enforcement agencies from across the state ran alongside athletes during Thursday's run.\", \"from\": 577, \"to\": 768, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"(It's great) to have everybody come together and remember him,\\\" said Investigator Chad Minuto with the Genesee County Sheriff's Office.\", \"from\": 770, \"to\": 906, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 853, \"end\": 857, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chad\", \"score\": 0.9987562057034027, \"rank\": 0.000939577241710912, \"text\": \"Chad\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chad\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chad\"}, {\"begin\": 889, \"end\": 896, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sheriffs_in_the_United_States\", \"score\": 0.9452424413640487, \"rank\": 0.05524674555952855, \"text\": \"Sheriff\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sheriffs_in_the_United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sheriffs_in_the_United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have been trying to do that since his passing, and we do not ever want to forget his memory, so this is just another way to bring a tribute to a great guy and a great officer.\\\"\", \"from\": 907, \"to\": 1087, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The torch run is an annual tradition that helps raise money and awareness for the Special Olympics of New York, which is taking place in Ithaca this weekend.\", \"from\": 1089, \"to\": 1246, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1191, \"end\": 1199, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"score\": 0.9999812171193566, \"rank\": 1.4282790137887945e-05, \"text\": \"New York\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_Ci